				<h2 class="title icon icon0">
					Re: Should online games allow use of assistive technologies for the handicapped?
				</h2>
				

						
						
				<div class="content">
					<div id="post_message_1755123">
						<blockquote class="postcontent restore ">
							ADA applies to sports but not really since all employees have to be able to perform essential functions reasonably.  If a player could do that with their disability, they would be on the field.  <br />
<br />
Games though are not telecommunications or public accommodations or employment.  ADA does not apply to players.
						</blockquote>
					</div>

					
				</div>
			</div>
			
			<div class="after_content">
				
                                       
                                 
				
		        		<blockquote class="signature restore"><div class="signaturecontainer"><img src="http://img.photobucket.com/albums/v319/DmitrytheWizzy/signature-LQEK4TQ3.png" border="0" alt="" /></div></blockquote>
				
                                        
